  "detailed_description": "This is a text-based multiplayer online MMO that takes you back to the world of martial arts, allowing you to experience your own martial arts life in the Jianghu.<br />\r\nIn the game, you will play the role of a wandering knight in the Jianghu, where you can learn martial arts in different sects and make friends. You can choose to be a hero, upholding justice and righteousness, or indulge in reckless behavior to experience a different life. In World, there is nothing you can't think of or do. It's a world of endless possibilities.",
